title: Beekeeper Singed
body: I was wondering if anyone knows what happened to Beekeeper Singed, was it just me or did it seem like it was only out for like a week ? Why can't I buy it anymore & how much was it ? That seems like a skin that would always be in shop idk.

replies.body: It was held back cause it was bugged. Idk what the current situation is.
